29
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:51,259
to help in the battle against mosquito-transmitted diseases.

30
00:02:51,939 --> 00:02:55,439
And so, you know, it's something that caught my eye many years ago.

31
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:59,780
I was directed to it, and I've been working with it my whole life, academic life now.

32
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:03,860
Can we go back a little step to dengue fever?

33
00:03:03,939 --> 00:03:09,039
It's probably the most known mosquito-borne virus that you work with,

34
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,259
