53
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,759
It doesn't infect people.

54
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:21,779
It's called Wolbachia.

55
00:04:22,339 --> 00:04:28,019
And we found that about 50% of insects carry this bacteria naturally,

56
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:31,839
but not the mosquitoes that do all this disease transmission to people.

57
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:38,100
