You know, it's got a lot of very desirable,

77
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,500
As you said, it doesn't kill the mosquitoes.

78
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,339
It just makes them harmless to people.

79
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:46,899
So they stay within the role.

80
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:50,000
If there is such a role that they might play in the ecosystem,

81
00:05:50,540 --> 00:05:55,839
we're not spreading toxins around like insecticides that aren't that effective anyway,

82
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:59,439
but have a lot of knock-on effects into the environment.

83
00:05:59,939 --> 00:06:03,740
So it's a really targeted green intervention.

84
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:07,560
But what I like most about it is that it self-sustains

85
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,259
so that once we deploy it,

86
00:06:09,259 --> 00:06:09,379
we don't have to re-deploy it.

87
00:06:09,379 --> 00:06:09,660
We don't have to re-deploy it.

88
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:09,720
We don't have to re-deploy it.

89
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:09,800
We don't have to re-deploy it.

90
